  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Based on the movie animation of Street Fighter II, this game takes place of a cyborg that M. Bison constructed to be the final contender of Street Fitgher tournament. As the games goes on you'll see different scenes of the animated movie and you need to take photos of exact moments to improve the cyborg and even learn special movements. After all this your cyborg can have a fight on the old-fashionated way of SF remaks, a 1-on-1 fight against Ryu.",
